00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:19.960
Weigui!

00:02:23.190 --> 00:02:23.710
Weigui!

00:02:25.030 --> 00:02:25.560
Weigui.

00:02:28.150 --> 00:02:28.710
Weigui.

00:02:31.310 --> 00:02:32.430
Where did he go?

00:02:35.470 --> 00:02:35.960
Oh, no.

00:02:36.430 --> 00:02:37.000
The time has changed.

00:02:37.710 --> 00:02:39.430
We must sell more fish today.

00:02:39.430 --> 00:02:40.190
Right.

