Madam Wang's daughter is about to get married.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:46.960
[Xiangrui Boutique]
Make sure you attend it.

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:47.710
Yes.

00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:48.520
- Congratulations. - Congratulations.

00:02:48.520 --> 00:02:49.120
Thank you.

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:49.800
Thank you.

00:03:03.380 --> 00:03:10.220
[The Two Sides of Qiankun]

00:03:12.120 --> 00:03:12.840
You're back.

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:15.750
And this is...

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:17.080
He

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:18.360
is Ye Zhixin.

00:03:18.710 --> 00:03:19.800
He once saved Weigui and me.

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:21.800
Weigui is gone.

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:22.750
He is not here to begin with.

00:03:23.870 --> 00:03:24.360
Besides,

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:26.280
I had an important revelation.

00:03:27.750 --> 00:03:28.280
There are

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:29.680
two Qiankun Villages.

00:03:30.750 --> 00:03:32.310
Two Qiankun Villages?

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:34.120
You

00:03:34.630 --> 00:03:35.710
remind me of something.

00:03:36.430 --> 00:03:37.590
I read

00:03:37.590 --> 00:03:39.150
about this mysterious village

00:03:39.560 --> 00:03:40.910
that has two sides.

00:03:41.910 --> 00:03:42.360
Right.

00:03:42.590 --> 00:03:43.430
It says here

00:03:43.630 --> 00:03:44.870
that after every hour,

00:03:45.030 --> 00:03:47.000
you'll go back to the other side.

00:03:47.150 --> 00:03:47.560
Exactly.

00:03:48.150 --> 00:03:49.280
It is as you said.

00:03:49.870 --> 00:03:50.870
We now need

00:03:51.240 --> 00:03:51.840
to find a way

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:53.560
to enter the other Qiankun Village.

00:03:55.590 --> 00:03:56.400
It will be difficult.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:57.750
They won't

00:03:58.150 --> 00:03:59.750
tell outsiders the secret to it easily.

00:04:08.540 --> 00:04:10.240
[Bird]

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:10.960
Bird?

00:04:16.510 --> 00:04:17.240
I get it now.

00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:18.240
Weigui

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:20.190
must have left this clue for us.

00:04:22.310 --> 00:04:23.000
Could it be

00:04:23.430 --> 00:04:24.630
the Bird is the key?

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:26.120
Right.

00:04:26.830 --> 00:04:28.560
When day and night swap,

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:30.120
we can hear the bird's chirp.

00:04:32.920 --> 00:04:33.630
I see.

00:04:34.040 --> 00:04:35.680
We must find the bird

00:04:36.070 --> 00:04:37.600
to enter the other Qiankun Village.

00:04:37.870 --> 00:04:38.270
Let's go.

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:43.240
Xiaohua.

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:45.190
[Tea]
How come you're so sure it's the bird?

00:04:45.630 --> 00:04:47.040
When I arrived at the Chief's abode,

00:04:47.160 --> 00:04:48.160
I noticed that the bird was different.

00:04:49.270 --> 00:04:49.830
Chief.

00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:56.800
What a weird village.

00:04:57.430 --> 00:04:58.120
Let's save

00:04:58.600 --> 00:04:59.510
Weigui first.

00:05:01.050 --> 00:05:01.930
[Yixiang Eatery]
The pigeon is there.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:13.390
Drink my concoction

00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:15.830
and you will become my thrall.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:18.600
Stop!

00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:21.920
Weigui.

00:05:22.950 --> 00:05:23.430
Weigui?

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:24.920
How...

00:05:25.390 --> 00:05:26.390
How did you come here?

00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:30.950
We saw through your trick.

00:05:31.750 --> 00:05:32.800
We found the pigeon

00:05:33.070 --> 00:05:34.600
that could change the time.

00:05:39.740 --> 00:05:45.260
[Yixiang Eatery]

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:49.510
Weigui.

00:05:52.750 --> 00:05:53.310
Weigui.

00:05:53.870 --> 00:05:54.430
Come.

00:05:54.950 --> 00:05:56.070
You're finally awake.

00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:57.190
I thought

00:05:57.430 --> 00:05:58.600
you'd wake up a few days later.

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:00.750
I...

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:03.120
You can't remember anything at all?

00:06:05.920 --> 00:06:06.600
Two days ago,

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:08.190
we couldn't find you

00:06:08.750 --> 00:06:10.120
[Bird]
but we saw what you wrote.

00:06:10.630 --> 00:06:11.270
We realized

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:13.070
that it was the key to Qiankun Village's secret.

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:13.560
Stop!

00:06:14.240 --> 00:06:15.560
When we found the chief,

00:06:15.950 --> 00:06:17.070
your life was hanging by a thread.

00:06:18.070 --> 00:06:19.920
Ye intervened

00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:21.920
and Chief fled in fear.

00:06:25.190 --> 00:06:26.190
After searching the place,

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:27.630
Xiaohua found the prescription for the antidote.

00:06:27.630 --> 00:06:28.270
I found it.

00:06:28.480 --> 00:06:29.920
Then, we cured your cold toxin.

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:31.560
Weigui.

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:33.510
I saved your life.

00:06:34.040 --> 00:06:35.190
Have you seen how terrified

00:06:35.190 --> 00:06:36.630
the chief was when he saw me?

00:06:36.680 --> 00:06:38.510
You're so lucky to have

00:06:38.510 --> 00:06:39.680
a protective leader like me.

00:06:40.040 --> 00:06:40.560
What do you think?

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:41.560
As your leader,

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.000
I am a man of my word.

00:06:43.800 --> 00:06:44.630
Deeply

00:06:44.870 --> 00:06:45.720
in love

00:06:46.190 --> 00:06:47.000
and

00:06:47.240 --> 00:06:47.920
passionate.

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:51.160
Like two cords in...

00:06:51.750 --> 00:06:52.510
What are you writing?

00:06:54.680 --> 00:06:55.270
Nothing.

00:06:59.310 --> 00:07:00.830
They share a strong bond,

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:02.510
like two cords in harmony.

00:07:02.630 --> 00:07:03.920
I see.

00:07:04.430 --> 00:07:05.480
You're inventing a love story

00:07:05.600 --> 00:07:07.070
out of us three to sell it for money.

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:09.390
You've tainted the pure friendship between us.

00:07:09.870 --> 00:07:10.600
I

00:07:10.830 --> 00:07:11.870
cannot let this slide.

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:12.750
I...

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:13.800
Well,

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:15.070
we can split the profit 40-60.

00:07:15.070 --> 00:07:15.950
40-60?

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.510
Who gets 40 and who gets 60?

00:07:18.070 --> 00:07:18.560
Wait, no.

00:07:19.600 --> 00:07:21.040
I'm not materialistic like that.

00:07:21.190 --> 00:07:22.270
This isn't about money.

00:07:23.830 --> 00:07:24.680
But I suppose

00:07:24.950 --> 00:07:26.070
I can give it back to you.

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:29.750
I take 80, you take 20.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.270
Why are you on her side?

00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:39.870
Miss Xiaohua,

00:07:40.120 --> 00:07:41.830
it must have been tough for you to travel alone in the martial arts world.

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:44.160
She just wants to make a living.

00:07:44.830 --> 00:07:45.600
Besides,

00:07:46.070 --> 00:07:47.000
without her,

00:07:47.600 --> 00:07:49.680
I wouldn't have been alive.

00:07:55.750 --> 00:07:56.510
Xiaohua,

00:07:57.920 --> 00:07:59.120
I'm sure in the future,

00:07:59.830 --> 00:08:01.680
you'll be part of Baixiao Hall.

00:08:10.160 --> 00:08:11.430
Truth be told, Ye,

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:13.630
I do have the Skysplitter fragment.

00:08:13.750 --> 00:08:15.750
I just didn't know that the chief would turn the villagers

00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:17.560
against us in order to get it.

00:08:18.190 --> 00:08:19.120
The Skysplitter fragment

00:08:19.270 --> 00:08:20.720
has caused many conflicts

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:21.830
in the martial arts world.

00:08:22.310 --> 00:08:23.000
This hardly surprises me.

00:08:27.070 --> 00:08:27.630
Weigui.

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:28.950
Now that you're awake,

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:30.120
and we're all safe,

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:31.800
let's get out of here quickly

00:08:32.030 --> 00:08:33.150
in case we get into any trouble.

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:39.360
Thank you, Ye, for helping us again.

00:08:39.720 --> 00:08:41.080
That way, we get to keep the fragment safe.

00:08:41.270 --> 00:08:41.720
I

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:43.000
will repay your kindness in the future.

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:43.870
You're welcome, Lei.

00:08:44.550 --> 00:08:45.670
I have business to attend to.

00:08:46.200 --> 00:08:46.910
Allow me

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:48.440
to bid farewell here.

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:49.600
Take care.

00:08:49.870 --> 00:08:50.390
Ye.

00:08:51.390 --> 00:08:52.440
It's dangerous out there.

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:53.670
Why don't you

00:08:53.870 --> 00:08:54.720
travel with us?

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:55.600
We can

00:08:56.030 --> 00:08:57.030
look after each other.

00:08:59.240 --> 00:08:59.790
No need.

00:09:01.390 --> 00:09:03.600
I was told that someone in Qingyin Parlor has the Skysplitter fragment.

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:05.270
You should go there now.

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:06.750
May we

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:09.080
meet again.

00:09:28.600 --> 00:09:29.550
Ye

00:09:30.080 --> 00:09:31.320
looks fragile,

00:09:31.960 --> 00:09:33.120
but he's very strong.

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:38.360
And why didn't he get the Skysplitter fragment on his own?

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:40.270
He

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.030
is stronger than us.

00:09:46.500 --> 00:09:50.460
[Yixiang Eatery]

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:52.360
I cannot stay here anymore.

00:09:55.550 --> 00:09:56.600
Greetings, Sect Leader.

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.480
I wasn't expecting you.

00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:00.390
At ease.

00:10:00.870 --> 00:10:01.440
Madam,

00:10:01.790 --> 00:10:02.600
I have been

00:10:02.910 --> 00:10:04.030
collecting herbs for years.

00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:05.030
My research

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:06.200
is about to succeed.

00:10:06.510 --> 00:10:07.390
Do not worry, Madam.

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:08.600
I will find a way

00:10:08.670 --> 00:10:09.510
to cure you.

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:11.960
What have you done to the villagers?

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:14.240
I did that for you.

00:10:16.550 --> 00:10:17.270
Unfortunately,

00:10:18.270 --> 00:10:19.510
you used the wrong method.

00:10:49.630 --> 00:10:50.120
So,

00:10:50.550 --> 00:10:51.240
you must be hungry.

00:10:51.910 --> 00:10:52.360
Come.

00:11:03.600 --> 00:11:04.510
Thank you for saving my life.

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:07.150
You're my sidekick.

00:11:07.440 --> 00:11:09.000
I'm in charge of you.

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:12.240
No need to thank me either.

00:11:12.550 --> 00:11:13.720
I was paid for it anyway.

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:16.000
Oh, Weigui,

00:11:16.390 --> 00:11:17.670
back then, we were in danger,

00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:18.790
so I didn't have time to ask you.

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:20.390
Are you searching for the Skysplitter fragment

00:11:20.670 --> 00:11:21.960
so that you can rule the world as well?

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:25.910
No.

00:11:26.960 --> 00:11:28.000
I knew I was right about you.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:30.030
You're not power-hungry like the others.

00:11:33.750 --> 00:11:35.000
Then why do you want

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:35.720
the fragment?

00:11:44.910 --> 00:11:45.670
Greetings, Sect Leader.

00:11:49.720 --> 00:11:51.120
Have you saved the villagers?

00:11:51.630 --> 00:11:53.600
[Left Emissary]
Qiankun Village has been dealt with.

00:11:54.150 --> 00:11:54.910
Good.

00:11:55.790 --> 00:11:56.320
But

00:11:56.480 --> 00:11:57.720
I would like to seek clarification.

00:12:00.270 --> 00:12:01.870
The chief took over the village

00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:03.600
so that he could study medicine for your ailment.

00:12:04.030 --> 00:12:05.120
Why must you...

00:12:07.550 --> 00:12:09.960
Qin Aoxiong would kill innocents just to set up a trap

00:12:10.440 --> 00:12:12.720
to obtain the Skysplitter fragment.

00:12:14.030 --> 00:12:15.630
What happened to Qiankun Village was even worse.

00:12:16.510 --> 00:12:18.550
The whole village was sacrificed.

00:12:20.030 --> 00:12:22.440
Everyone plots and schemes to extreme lengths

00:12:22.600 --> 00:12:23.550
to get

00:12:23.550 --> 00:12:24.510
the fragment.

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:26.270
Little did they know,

00:12:26.870 --> 00:12:29.080
it might just be a lure released by that person.

00:12:30.150 --> 00:12:31.320
Master told us

00:12:32.000 --> 00:12:32.870
that the Skysplitter

00:12:33.550 --> 00:12:34.840
was a divine sword forged

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:37.200
by the ancient forge deity using Mountainfort Copper.

00:12:38.150 --> 00:12:39.480
It is very durable,

00:12:39.910 --> 00:12:41.150
and probably will never shatter.

00:12:41.480 --> 00:12:43.240
But something doesn't make sense to me.

00:12:43.510 --> 00:12:45.270
Who was Qin Aoxiong working for?

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:46.150
And who

00:12:46.270 --> 00:12:48.790
told the chief about the Skysplitter fragment?

00:12:52.120 --> 00:12:53.030
I swear it wasn't me.

00:12:56.790 --> 00:12:57.600
It's okay.

00:13:00.550 --> 00:13:01.390
At this point,

00:13:02.390 --> 00:13:03.510
perhaps only he

00:13:03.960 --> 00:13:05.840
knows where Skysplitter is.

00:13:20.870 --> 00:13:22.080
I want the Skysplitter fragment

00:13:22.240 --> 00:13:23.360
so that I can have my answer.

00:13:24.910 --> 00:13:25.670
Answer?

00:13:30.630 --> 00:13:32.510
Why do you desire so much to be

00:13:32.670 --> 00:13:33.360
the top swordsman then?

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:35.270
My master told me to do that.

00:13:35.790 --> 00:13:37.440
I might as well train myself in the martial arts world.

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:40.000
Maybe one day,

00:13:41.000 --> 00:13:42.080
I can find

00:13:42.390 --> 00:13:43.510
the heart of sword like my master did

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:44.480
and unsheathe my sword.

00:13:49.150 --> 00:13:49.840
Oh, Weigui.

00:13:50.150 --> 00:13:51.270
Your swordsmanship is excellent.

00:13:51.790 --> 00:13:53.360
Who taught you that?

00:13:54.910 --> 00:13:56.630
I bought a random sword manual,

00:13:57.270 --> 00:13:58.390
studied it thoroughly,

00:13:58.720 --> 00:13:59.960
and practiced every day.

00:14:01.150 --> 00:14:02.360
I owe my accomplishments today

00:14:02.510 --> 00:14:03.550
to my persistent training.

00:14:04.080 --> 00:14:05.480
That's all it takes to be this strong?

00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:06.550
I'm impressed.

00:14:08.630 --> 00:14:09.320
But

00:14:09.600 --> 00:14:10.720
I've also heard

00:14:10.960 --> 00:14:11.750
that an ordinary martial monk

00:14:11.960 --> 00:14:13.360
who practices Dragon King Fist for 50 years

00:14:13.390 --> 00:14:14.840
can create fire from an ember

00:14:15.080 --> 00:14:16.000
or sprout a flower from a rock.

00:14:16.550 --> 00:14:17.240
I believe

00:14:17.750 --> 00:14:18.550
as long

00:14:19.030 --> 00:14:20.080
as I practice diligently,

00:14:20.390 --> 00:14:21.670
I will become

00:14:21.750 --> 00:14:23.200
the strongest swordsman.

00:14:23.200 --> 00:14:26.460
♪The fearless youths band together and travel the world♪

00:14:26.460 --> 00:14:32.860
♪With a carefree heroic spirit, it's never lonely with a confidant♪

00:15:08.440 --> 00:15:12.120
♪How can I make peace when time♪

00:15:12.480 --> 00:15:15.240
♪Only leaves me with my shadow?♪

00:15:16.680 --> 00:15:20.200
♪Yet the intertwining bonds in my life♪

00:15:20.400 --> 00:15:23.480
♪Render me blind♪

00:15:24.880 --> 00:15:28.400
♪I was once naive and innocent♪

00:15:28.800 --> 00:15:31.680
♪Seeking a soul with whom to dance♪

